      { question: "A chest tube accidentally disconnects from the drainage system. Priority action?", options: ["Clamp the chest tube immediately", "Submerge the tube end in sterile water to create a water seal", "Reconnect without any protective measures", "Remove the chest tube"], correct: 1, rationale: "Submerging the tube end in sterile water creates an emergency water seal, allowing air to exit the pleural space while preventing air entry. CLAMPING a tube with an air leak risks tension pneumothorax." }
